title: Kiss: Woman, Person, Medium-Light Skin Tone

description: Depicts a romantic kiss between a woman and another person, with a medium-light skin tone. It signifies affection, romance, and love.

Apple's design emphasizes a gentle glow and realistic lighting, giving the emoji a warm and intimate feel. It's a sweet and romantic symbol used to convey affection, love, or a charming greeting in digital exchanges on Apple devices.
